column4: Major earthquake hits Kathmandu. Major one.
Huge earthquake in Kathmandu. I'm terrified.
Major earthquake hits  Kathmandu. Major one.
Roads cracked! Walls down! Sky full of dust! #earthquake #Kathmandu
[TRANS] Nepal library fund-raising charity photo exhibition 25th April, Saturday, 3pm Bundang-gu (cont)
Locals dragged me into a cafe in patan Durban square. A little more open. But I'm scared. Aftershocks.
Earthquake in Kathmandu! Everyone in the streets. That's a new one for me!  #earthquake   #survived
Never experience an  #earthquake  like this in  #kathmandu ! Stay safe people !
